Package com.Bean

Class BeanContactDetails

java.lang.Object
com.Bean.BeanContactDetails
public class BeanContactDetails extends Object
Represents the contact details of a person. This class encapsulates various attributes related to a contact, including name, email, phone number, and other personal details.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sahana
